<title>ION Financial Model — Summary &amp; Analysis</title>
<meta name="description" content="A summary and analysis of the Pessimistic ION Financial Model (revised, formula-driven): GMV ramp, revenue build, profitability path, cash, and a critique of the load-bearing assumptions." />
